{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setLanguage:","role":"symbol","title":"setLanguage:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setLanguage:"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setLanguage:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"language","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The language code (e.g., “en”, “de”, “fr”, “es”) or nil to reset to device language","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"language"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Override the device language for Pushwoosh to enable:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sending notifications in a specific language"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Language-based segmentation"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Supporting in-app language switching"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Must be a lowercase two-letter code according to ISO-639-1 standard."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Support in-app language selection:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class LanguageManager {","","    static let shared = LanguageManager()","","    var currentLanguage: String {","        didSet {","            applyLanguageChange()","        }","    }","","    func applyLanguageChange() {","        \/\/ Update Pushwoosh language for targeted notifications","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","","        \/\/ Update user tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"language\": currentLanguage,","            \"language_changed_date\": Date()","        ])","","        \/\/ Update app UI","        Bundle.setLanguage(currentLanguage)","        NotificationCenter.default.post(name: .languageDidChange, object: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"App language changed to: \\(currentLanguage)\")","    }","","    func resetToDeviceLanguage() {","        Pushwoosh.configure.setLanguage(nil)","        currentLanguage = Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\"","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"“zh” (Chinese), “ja” (Japanese), “ko” (Korean), “ru” (Russian)","type":"text"}]}]}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setlanguage:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setLanguage:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets custom application language for localized notifications."}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"